            "chunk_index": 1,
            "text": "116 OG No. 35, 5404 (August 31, 2020)\n\n[ REPUBLIC ACT NO. 11483, August 14, 2020 ]\n\nAN ACT CONVERTING THE STA. IGNACIA-GUIMBA PROVINCIAL ROAD IN THE PROVINCE OF TARLAC AND NUEVA ECIJA VIA GERONA-PURA ROAD STRETCHING FROM BARANGAY NAMBALAN, MUNICIPALITY OF STA. IGNACIA TO BARANGAY BUENAVISTA, MUNICIPALITY OF PURA, ALL IN THE PROVINCE OF TARLAC INTO A NATIONAL ROAD AND APPROPRIATING FUNDS THEREFOR\n\nBe it enacted by the Senate and House of Representatives of the Philippines in Congress assembled:\n\nSECTION 1. The Sta. Ignacia-Guimba Provincial Road in the provinces of Tarlac and Nueva Ecija via Gerona-Pura Road stretching from Barangay Nambalan, Municipality of Sta. Ignacia to Barangay Buenavista, Municipality of Pura, all in the Province of Tarlac is hereby converted into a national road.",
            "metadata": {
                "law_id": "RA_11483",
                "date": "August 14, 2020"
            }
        },
